            <p>
                Rodenstock is a leading German manufacturer of ophthalmic glasses and eyeglass frames. The company was founded in 1877 in Munich and now has over 4,000 employees worldwide, represented in over 80 countries with sales centers and distribution partners. Rodenstock maintains ophthalmic glass production in a total of 14 locations in 12 countries. One of them is our store which was founded in 2011.
            </p>
